&lt;p&gt;Hoodie provides a configuration file called &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;blog-config.js&lt;/code&gt;. In this file, you can configure blog, biography (profile), and utterance. The website settings you are currently viewing are as above.&lt;/p&gt;
